rows.label: tlk70000010_05_msg0001
rows.name:
Hey Laura. Would it kill you
to crack a smile? Cheer up!

rows.label: tlk70000010_05_msg0002
rows.name:
Maybe you're tense. Relax.
Just let go of all that
tension in your shoulders.

rows.label: tlk70000010_05_msg0003
rows.name:
Just remember, that you have a
really great support network
around you. People you can trust.

rows.label: tlk70000010_05_msg0004
rows.name:
You need to learn to rely on them,
and to see yourself the way they
see you. Love yourself, girl!

rows.label: tlk70000010_05_msg0005
rows.name:
Hey, by the way, have you met a special
someone lately, Laura? That's the vibe
I'm getting off you right now.

rows.label: tlk70000010_05_msg0006
rows.name:
So who is this dude
anyway? Someone I know?

rows.label: tlk70000010_05_msg0007
rows.name:
The curiousity's just burning
right up. Come on, 'fess up!

rows.label: tlk70000010_05_msg0008
rows.name:
Well, you don't want to tell me now,
fine. Maybe you don't want to jinx it.
But tell me when you're back, OK?
